·         YearMonthShort into Rows

·         Avg.Tickets Per Day

   MoM%TicketPerDay =

  = VAR PRE  = CALCULATE ([Avg. Tickets Per Day], DATEADD ('Calendar'[Date], -1, MONTH))

VAR CUR = CALCULATE ([Avg. Tickets per Day])

RETURN

IF (ISBLANK (PRE), 0, (CUR - PRE) /PRE)

 

·         AvgFirstRspHrs

·         MoM%FirstRspHrs

  = VAR PRE = CALCULATE ([*AvgFirstRspHrs_Full], DATEADD ('Calendar'[Date], -1, MONTH))

VAR CUR = CALCULATE ([*AvgFirstRspHrs_Full])

RETURN

IF (ISBLANK (PRE), 0, (CUR - PRE) /PRE)

·        1stConRRate

·         MoM%1stConRRate

  = VAR PRE = CALCULATE ([*1stContactResolutionRate], DATEADD ('Calendar'[Date], -1, MONTH))

VAR CUR = CALCULATE ([*1stContactResolutionRate])

RETURN

IF (ISBLANK (PRE), 0, (CUR - PRE) /PRE)

 

·         AvgDaysOpen

·         AvgTimeToCloseDays

·         MoM%TimetoClose   

 = VAR PRE = CALCULATE (SUM (ZendeskTicketSystem[TimeToCloseDays]), DATEADD ('calendar'[Date], -1, MONTH))

VAR CUR = CALCULATE (SUM (ZendeskTicketSystem[TimeToCloseDays]))

RETURN

IF (ISBLANK (PRE), 0, (CUR - PRE) /PRE)
